## Methodology

- Used INNER JOINs to connect related tables using suspect_id
- Applied filters to isolate suspects matching each clue
- Used LIKE with wildcards to search alibi text
- Compared phone locations and alibi locations to identify inconsistencies
- Combined multiple query results with UNION ALL
- Used GROUP BY and HAVING COUNT(*) = 5 to find the suspect appearing in every clue result set

